---
title: Warm Roasted Tomato & Lentil Salad with Feta, Aubergine, Rocket and Croutons
description: Looking for a tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Tomato & Lentil Salad with Feta in just 20 minutes for a balanced and tasty dinnertime.
